'''PSR B1509-58'''是一顆[[脈衝星|脈衝星]]，位在[[圓規座|圓規座]]，1982年由[[愛因斯坦衛星|愛因斯坦衛星]]發現<ref>Seward F. D., Harnden Jr F. R., 1982, ApJ, 256, L45</ref>，距離地球大約17,000[[光年|光年]]遠。它的年齡約1,700歲<ref>{{cite web|author=|url=http://chandra.harvard.edu/photo/2009/b1509/how_old.html|title=How Old Is It?|date=2009-04-03|publisher=[[Harvard-Smithsonian_Center_for_Astrophysics|Harvard-Smithsonian Center for Astrophysics]]|accessdate=2016-07-31|archive-date=2014-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110192627/http://chandra.harvard.edu/photo/2009/b1509/how_old.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，附近的[[星雲|星雲]]橫跨約150光年<ref>{{cite web|author=|url=http://chandra.harvard.edu/photo/2009/b1509/|title=PSR B1509-58: A Young Pulsar Shows its Hand|date=2009-04-03|publisher=[[Harvard|Harvard]]|accessdate=2016-07-31|archive-date=2010-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100331104920/http://chandra.harvard.edu/photo/2009/b1509/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

NASA描述這顆脈衝星類似「一隻宇宙之手」<ref name=cnn>{{cite web|author=|url=http://www.cnn.com/2009/TECH/space/04/14/space.hand/index.html?iref=mpstoryview=|title=NASA photos show giant cosmic hand|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=2009-04-14|accessdate=2016-07-31|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303165418/http://www.cnn.com/2009/TECH/space/04/14/space.hand/index.html?iref=mpstoryview=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

